<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Komunikacija</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T"
        crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.js" integrity="sha256-2Kok7MbOyxpgUVvAk/HJ2jigOSYS2auK4Pfzbm7uH60=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link href="/src/style.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
    <script src="./src/list.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <div style="padding: 50px">
        <h1>Портал за комуникацију и размену информација станара зграде у улици Горана Ђорђевића Пиште бр. 17</h1>
        <br>

        <form method="POST">
            <div class="form-group">

                <label style="font-size: 22px">Унесите Вашу поруку</label>
                <br>
                <input type="text" name="poruka" style="width: 500px; height: 100px; font-size: 22px;"   class="form-control" id="poruka" placeholder="Унесите поруку...." required>
                <br>

            </div>

            <button style="font-size: 22px" type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Пошаљите поруку</button>

            <a href="/logout" style="font-size: 22px; float:right;" type="submit" class="btn btn-info">Log out</a>

        </form>


        <table class="table table-sm" style="font-size: 22px">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th scope="col">Корисник</th>
                    <th scope="col">Порука</th>
                    <th scope="col">Време</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>

            <% for(let i=0; i<podaci.length; i++){ %>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <%= podaci[i].korisnik %>
                    </td> 
                    <td>
                        <%= podaci[i].poruka %>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <%= podaci[i].vreme %>
                    </td>
                    

                </tr>
                <% } %><br>

            

        </table>
    </div>


</body>

</html>